#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/dev/skills/design-and-build/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/js-cache-function-results.md
M|rules|title: Cache Repeated Function Calls
M|rules|impact: MEDIUM
M|rules|impactDescription: avoid redundant computation
M|rules|tags: javascript, cache, memoization, performance
M|rules|Use a module-level Map to cache function results when the same function is called repeatedly with the same inputs during render.
M|rules|**Incorrect (redundant computation):**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|function ProjectList({ projects }: { projects: Project[] }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|{projects.map(project => {
M|rules|// slugify() called 100+ times for same project names
M|rules|const slug = slugify(project.name)
M|rules|return <ProjectCard key={project.id} slug={slug} />
M|rules|})}
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (cached results):**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|// Module-level cache
M|rules|const slugifyCache = new Map<string, string>()
M|rules|function cachedSlugify(text: string): string {
M|rules|if (slugifyCache.has(text)) {
M|rules|return slugifyCache.get(text)!
M|rules|}
M|rules|const result = slugify(text)
M|rules|slugifyCache.set(text, result)
M|rules|return result
M|rules|}
M|rules|function ProjectList({ projects }: { projects: Project[] }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|{projects.map(project => {
M|rules|// Computed only once per unique project name
M|rules|const slug = cachedSlugify(project.name)
M|rules|return <ProjectCard key={project.id} slug={slug} />
M|rules|})}
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Simpler pattern for single-value functions:**
M|rules|```typescript
M|rules|let isLoggedInCache: boolean | null = null
M|rules|function isLoggedIn(): boolean {
M|rules|if (isLoggedInCache !== null) {
M|rules|return isLoggedInCache
M|rules|}
M|rules|isLoggedInCache = doc.cookie.includes('auth=')
M|rules|return isLoggedInCache
M|rules|}
M|rules|// Clear cache when auth changes
M|rules|function onAuthChange() {
M|rules|isLoggedInCache = null
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|Use a Map (not a hook) so it works everywhere: utilities, event handlers, not just React components.
M|rules|Reference: [How we made the Vercel Dashboard twice as fast](https://vercel.com/blog/how-we-made-the-vercel-dashboard-twice-as-fast)